data.description: Desirable location, sitting on over 6 acres of park-like common acre in Shalimar Sub! Community tennis courts and pool! This beautiful townhome has been completely remodeled.  Open living and kitchen which features granite counters, stainless appliances, gas cooktop and double ovens.  Enjoy the amazing views of the bogus and the foothills out the large picture windows.  Huge main level master with an oversized walk-in closest. Second bedroom on the main floor has sliding doors out to the hot tub and brank new deck.  Upstairs is a private oasis with a loft and 3rd bedroom and a full bathroom.  This home is loaded with storage, new rain gutters, newly installed epoxy floor in garage with a pull down ladder system leading to attic storage. Step into the backyard on the beautiful new deck and enjoy the view of the large common area park and the Boise mountain range!
